      <title>英国将制裁从叙利亚实体提升到新领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/uk-lifts-sanctions-from-syria-entities-in-boost-to-new-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国从批准的机构名单中删除了叙利亚中央银行和其他23个实体，这是对前总统巴沙尔·阿萨德（Bashar al-Assad）推翻后对该国新政府的认可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/uk-lifts-sanctions-from-syria-entities-in-boost-to-new-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 15:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普可能会推迟对商品的关税，USMCA下的服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-likely-to-defer-tariffs-on-goods-services-under-usmca</link>
      <description><![CDATA[商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）说，唐纳德·特朗普总统可能会将他对加拿大和墨西哥的25％关税归因于北美贸易协定所涵盖的所有商品和服务，称为USMCA，这是美国两个最大贸易伙伴的潜在重大缓刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-likely-to-defer-tariffs-on-goods-services-under-usmca</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 15:15:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队通过询问谁赢得2020年大选来测试求职者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-white-house-vets-job-candidates-on-loyalty-to-the-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，白宫正在采访中对潜在的候选工作候选人测试，以确保他们足够忠于唐纳德·特朗普总统及其第二任议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-white-house-vets-job-candidates-on-loyalty-to-the-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰的Zaluzhnyi说，我们正在“摧毁”世界秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ukraine-s-zaluzhnyi-says-us-is-destroying-the-world-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰前最高军事指挥官警告说，美国正在“摧毁”世界既定的命令，对唐纳德·特朗普对俄罗斯的态度进行了彻底的批评，这种措施有可能阻碍沃迪米·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）总统企图修复关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/ukraine-s-zaluzhnyi-says-us-is-destroying-the-world-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 14:48:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普花了冻结在赠款上，贷款被另一位法官封锁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-spending-freeze-on-grants-loans-blocked-by-another-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官发布了一项长期命令，阻止了唐纳德·特朗普总统的争议，以冻结国会批准的贷款，赠款和其他向美国接收者支付的贷款和其他付款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-spending-freeze-on-grants-loans-blocked-by-another-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 14:39:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国贸易赤字在特朗普关税之前飙升至记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-trade-deficit-surges-to-a-record-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当公司争先恐后地从海外获得货物，唐纳德·特朗普总统对美国最大的贸易伙伴征收关税，美国的贸易赤字在一月份扩大到了记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/us-trade-deficit-surges-to-a-record-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚叛国罪调查针对俄罗斯有联系的极右翼情节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/romania-detains-six-people-for-treason-in-russia-linked-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚检察官拘留了六名涉嫌计划推翻政府的人，因为当局担心在进行重要投票之前对外国干预的担心，当局削减了越来越右的右翼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/romania-detains-six-people-for-treason-in-russia-linked-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 08:59:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>主要共和党与特朗普疾病预防控制中心的疫苗观点不同意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/key-republican-concerned-about-trump-cdc-pick-s-vaccine-views</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅因州参议员苏珊·柯林斯（Susan Collins）说，她与唐纳德·特朗普总统的提名人“有分歧”，领导疾病控制与预防中心，这是对投票结果的温和共和党人的立场关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/key-republican-concerned-about-trump-cdc-pick-s-vaccine-views</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 00:53:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称为农业到加拿大的墨西哥关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-weighs-agriculture-carveouts-from-canada-mexico-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统正在考虑将某些农产品免于对加拿大和墨西哥征收的关税，这是政府周三采取的最新举动，以减轻某些部门的新进口税款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/trump-weighs-agriculture-carveouts-from-canada-mexico-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 22:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，库莫在纽约市长比赛中领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/cuomo-has-wide-lead-in-race-for-new-york-city-mayor-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，纽约州长安德鲁·库莫（Andrew Cuomo）在纽约市六月民主党市长初级竞赛中占据了领先的埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）和所有其他候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/cuomo-has-wide-lead-in-race-for-new-york-city-mayor-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 20:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
